### =====================================================================
### 竞赛通 - 管理后台 (admin) + 赛事方 (partner) 测试文件
### =====================================================================
### 用法: IntelliJ 打开本文件,顶部 ▶️ Run All Requests in File
### 前置:
###   1. 业务表已建,99-test-fixtures.sql 已导入
###   2. 97-disable-captcha-dev.sql 已跑(关闭 admin 登录验证码)
###   3. 96-grant-jst-partner-permissions.sql 已跑(给 jst_partner 角色赋权)
###   4. ruoyi-admin 启动在 8080
### 特点:
###   - admin 视角 + 赛事方视角的完整 CRUD + 状态机流转
###   - wx 端测试在 wx-tests.http
### =====================================================================

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@contentType = application/json
### =====================================================================
### F9. 报名记录与表单快照 (jst-event / EnrollRecordController)
### 前置: fixture 中 8901=pending, 8902=approved, 8903=supplement，且 8201 属于 partner_f7_a
### =====================================================================

### F9-0. 赛事方 A 登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "partner_f7_a",
  "password": "admin123",
  "code": "1",
  "uuid": ""
}

> {%
client.global.set("partner_a_token", response.body.token);
%}

### F9-1. 赛事方查询报名列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/enroll/list?contestId=8201&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{partner_a_token}}

> {%
client.test("F9 报名列表查询成功", function() {
    client.assert(response.body.code === 200);
});
%}

### F9-2. 查看报名详情 (fixture 8901)
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/enroll/8901
Authorization: Bearer {{partner_a_token}}

> {%
client.test("F9 报名详情返回快照", function() {
    client.assert(response.body.code === 200);
    client.assert(response.body.data.formSnapshotJson, "应返回 formSnapshotJson");
});
%}

### F9-3. 审核通过 pending 报名 (fixture 8901)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/enroll/8901/audit
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{partner_a_token}}

{
  "result": "approved",
  "auditRemark": "资料完整，审核通过"
}

### F9-4. 已 approved 记录再次审核应失败 (fixture 8902)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/enroll/8902/audit
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{partner_a_token}}

{
  "result": "rejected",
  "auditRemark": "重复审核"
}

> {%
client.test("F9 已审核记录重复审核应失败", function() {
    client.assert(response.body.code !== 200);
});
%}

