### =====================================================================
### D. 赛事方入驻审核 (jst-organizer / PartnerApplyAdminController) - F5
### =====================================================================

### D1. 公开提交一份新申请(用唯一手机号)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/public/organizer/partner/apply
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "partnerName": "测试_admin侧入驻",
  "contactName": "测试_负责人",
  "contactMobile": "13800007777",
  "businessLicenseNo": "91110000ADM00001"
}

> {%
if (response.body.code === 200) {
    client.global.set("partner_apply_id", response.body.data.applyId);
    client.global.set("partner_apply_no", response.body.data.applyNo);
}
%}

### D2. admin 查询入驻申请列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/organizer/partner/apply/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### D3. admin 查申请详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/organizer/partner/apply/{{partner_apply_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### D4. admin 审核通过 → 创建 sys_user + jst_partner 角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/organizer/partner/apply/{{partner_apply_id}}/approve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "auditRemark": "材料齐全",
  "username": "partner_admin_test",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### D5. 重复 approve 应失败(状态机非法跃迁)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/organizer/partner/apply/{{partner_apply_id}}/approve
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "auditRemark": "重复",
  "username": "partner_admin_test2",
  "email": ""
}

> {%
client.test("重复 approve 应失败", function() {
    client.assert(response.body.code !== 200);
});
%}


