### G. 课程 admin (jst-event / CourseController) - F-COURSE
### =====================================================================

### G1. admin 创建课程草稿
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/course/add
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "courseName": "测试_admin侧课程",
  "courseType": "normal",
  "coverImage": "https://fixture.example.com/course-admin.jpg",
  "description": "admin-tests 创建的课程",
  "price": 99.00,
  "pointsPrice": 9900,
  "creatorType": "platform",
  "creatorId": 1,
  "visibleScope": "all"
}

> {%
