Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### G3. admin 审核通过课程
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/course/{{course_id}}/audit/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### G4. admin 上架课程
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/course/{{course_id}}/on
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### G5. admin 课程列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/course/list?pageNum=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### G6. 未审核通过的草稿不允许上架(用 fixture 7203 假设是 draft)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/course/7203/on
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

> {%
client.test("draft 上架应失败", function() {
    client.assert(response.body.code !== 200);
});
%}


