Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{ "auditRemark": "测试通过" }

### H6. admin 上线
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/contest/{{contest_id}}/online
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### H7. 越权: 赛事方 B 编辑 A 的赛事应失败
