### I2. admin 修改模板(版本 +1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/jst/event/form/template/save
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

{
  "templateId": {{template_id}},
  "templateName": "测试_admin侧模板_v2",
  "ownerType": "platform",
  "schemaJson": {
    "fields": [
      { "key": "name", "type": "text", "label": "姓名", "required": true },
      { "key": "gender", "type": "radio", "label": "性别", "required": true },
      { "key": "school", "type": "text", "label": "学校", "required": false }
    ]
  }
}

### I3. admin 提交审核
